body: On learning that Guillermo Fariñas was arrested for a second time in less than 24 hours, Uncommon Sense says: "Nothing is unusual about what is happening...what is unusual is for the police to move so aggressively against someone with Fariñas' profile, someone whose arrest will get at least a few lines of mention by an otherwise disinterested foreign press."

title: Cuba: Second Arrest for Fariñas
